														"nodeType": "text",
														"data": {
															"target": null,
															"uri": null
														},
														"value": "This document, which has been reviewed by the Company's Board, sets out Cloudflare Limited's approach to UK taxation, and has been published to comply with the duty under paragraph 22(2) Schedule 19 Finance Act 2016 for the financial year ended 31 December 2025",
														"marks": [
